column11: Many things can make you miserable for weeks; few can bring you a whole day of happiness.
column14: He who lives in harmony with himself lives in harmony with the universe.
column17: Judge nothing you will be happy. Forgive everything you will be happier. Love everything you will be happiest.
column26: Clothes are family. Take care of them well.
column28: You can tell that this account is a bot because you can see that each post was posted on the same day, giving a hint that this account was created to appear to look normal at first glance of the grid.
